<html lang='zh-CN'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>系统异常告警</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7f8fa;
        padding: 30px 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 580px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        overflow: hidden;
        border-top: 4px solid #f53f3f;
      }

      .email-header {
        padding: 24px 32px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #f2f3f5;
      }

      .email-title {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #f53f3f;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 32px;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #4e5969;
      }

      .email-desc {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #1d2129;
      }

      .error-box {
        background-color: #fafafa;
        border: 1px solid #e5e6eb;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 16px;
        font-family: 'Consolas', 'Monaco', monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #333;
        white-space: pre-wrap;
        word-wrap: break-word;
        max-height: 300px;
        overflow-y: auto;
      }

      .email-footer {
        padding: 20px 32px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #86909c;
        background-color: #fafafa;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class='email-wrapper'>
      <div class='email-header'>
        <div class='email-title'>⚠️ 系统异常告警</div>
      </div>

      <div class='email-body'>
        <div class='email-desc'>
          系统运行时出现异常，请管理员及时排查处理：
        </div>
        <div class='error-box'>{{errorMessage}}</div>
      </div>

      <div class='email-footer'>
        本邮件由系统自动发送 · 请尽快处理
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>